ng is there. If it said something like &quot;This site depicts fictional characters from an online game in vulgar and sexually explicit ways, do not enter if under 18&quot; Then parents could point that out to thier children and use it as an example that they should not be there.  <br>  <br> Thank you for understanding,  <br>  <br> A Povar Mom <br> <p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr align="right" valign="bottom"><td colspan=2 class="BoardRowB"><a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/help/default.asp?goto=faqs%2Easp%23lockedtopic">Locked Topic</a> | <a href="/active_topic_notify.asp?mes=10038477" class="BoardRowBLink">Active Topic Notification</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/pm_send.asp?usr=76154">Private Message</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/user_posts.asp?usr=76154">Post History</a></td></tr><tr align="left" valign="top" class="BoardRowA"><td class="BoardRowA" rowspan=3 width="17%"><a href=" http://users.ign.com/about/bran_pendragon?boards=vn " class="AuthorLink">bran_pendragon</a>&nbsp;<a href="/help/default.asp?goto=faqs%2Easp%23stars"><img align=absmiddle src=http://media.ign.com/boardimages/star.gif border=0 hspace=0 vspace=0 alt="172 posts"></a><br><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><!-- WISH & COLL STUFF --><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr class="BoardRowA"><td nowrap="false" class="BoardRowA"><a class="BoardRowBLink" href="http://users.ign.com/collection/bran_pendragon"><font size="1">collection (0)</font></a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="http://users.ign.com/wishlist/bran_pendragon"><font size="1">wishlist (0)</font></a></td></tr></table><!-- /WISH & COLL STUFF	--><span style="font-weight: bold;">Posts:</span> 172<br><span style="font-weight: bold;">Registered:</span> Apr 00<br></span><br></td><td class="BoardRowA" colspan=2 width="83%"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Date Posted:</span>&nbsp;3/19/01 9:03am&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bold;">Subject:</span> RE: A serious request of Triton</td></tr><tr valign=top><td class="BoardRo